<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">根据教育部统一部署，江西作为全国第四批启动高考综合改革的7省（区）之一，2024年将首次迎来新高考。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">今年1月，省教育厅印发了《江西省2024年普通高校招生文化考试安排和录取工作实施方案》。为帮助广大师生和家长系统了解和准确把握新高考文化考试和录取工作相关安排、政策措施、程序规则等，我们从今天起推出“江西省2024年普通高考综合改革热点问答”，为您具体解读。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>2024年普通高校招生文化考试与往年有什么区别？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>01 考试科目不同</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">新高考采用<strong>“3+1+2”模式</strong>。“3”为<strong>语文、数学、外语3门全国统考科目</strong>；“1”为首选科目，即<strong>物理、历史中的1门</strong>；“2”为再选科目，即<strong>思想政治、地理、化学、生物学4门科目中的2门</strong>。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940419026974.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051001.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940458061389.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051002.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940614062935.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051003.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">首选科目和再选科目由考生根据兴趣爱好和专业兴趣自主选择，学生的选择面扩大了。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>02 成绩构成不同</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">新高考考生的文化总成绩由<strong>语文、数学、外语3门全国统考科目成绩和3门选择性考试科目成绩组成，满分750分。</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">其中：</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>·</strong>语文、数学、外语三门统考科目每科满分150分，直接以卷面原始分数计入高考文化总成绩；</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>·</strong>考生选择的三门选考科目每科满分100分，首选科目（历史、物理2选1）直接以卷面原始分数计入高考文化总成绩；</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>·</strong>再选科目（思想政治、地理、化学、生物学4选2）以转换后的分数计入高考文化总成绩。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940767011195.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051004.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>2024年高考考试时间如何安排？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">语文考试时长为<strong>150分钟</strong>，数学和外语（含听力）考试时长均为<strong>120分钟</strong>。各选考科目考试时长均为<strong>75分钟</strong>，具体安排如下：</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940925061666.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051005.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong>有哪些官方平台可以获取高考信息？</strong></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">教育部“阳光高考”平台</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143940986033672.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051006.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">江西教育网</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941017054609.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051007.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">江西省教育考试院网</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941060046981.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051008.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">“江西省教育厅”微信公众号</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941097061699.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051009.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">以及各招生高校官方网站等。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941129046161.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051010.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">特别提醒考生和家长，在网上查询高校招生信息时，请认准<strong>“官网”</strong>标识，谨防山寨账号或网站骗局。</p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941160024656.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051011.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 18px; margin-bottom: 18px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(43, 51, 48); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, SimSun, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240531/1717143941190049287.jpg" title="jpg" alt="zrg2024051012.jpg" style="margin: 6px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;"/></p>